Likely edit site: `detect columns` currently collects pipeline input via `PipelineData::collect_string`, which reaches `ByteStream::into_string` and therefore checks child exit status.

### 1) `detect columns` uses `collect_string` directly

```rust
// crates/nu-command/src/strings/detect_columns.rs
